---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuoteForm from '../../components/QuoteForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Organic Moringa Powder - Certified from Ghana & Nigeria | Origin Direct"
  description="USDA and EU organic certified moringa powder from Ghana and Nigeria. 25-30% protein, pharmaceutical grade available. Enhanced testing protocols post-2026 FDA alert."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-900 via-brand-800 to-brand-700 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_60%,rgba(196,154,42,0.3),transparent_70%)]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-gold-light font-medium tracking-wide uppercase text-sm mb-4">Ghana &amp; Nigeria</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Organic Moringa Powder</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-brand-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Certified organic Moringa oleifera powder for supplements, health foods, and pharmaceutical applications. Enhanced safety protocols for every lot.
      </p>
      <a href="#quote-form" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gold hover:bg-gold-dark text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg text-lg">
        Request Quote
        <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Product Image -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
        <img
          src="/images/products/moringa.jpg"
          alt="Organic moringa powder from Ghana and Nigeria"
          class="w-full h-64 sm:h-80 object-cover"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-8">Overview</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 space-y-5">
        <p>
          Moringa oleifera has earned its reputation as a "superfood" with good reason: gram for gram, it contains more protein than eggs, more calcium than milk, more iron than spinach, and more vitamin A than carrots. The global moringa market is growing rapidly, driven by demand from health food brands, supplement manufacturers, and cosmetics companies across the US, Europe, and Asia.
        </p>
        <p>
          Origin Direct sources moringa from certified organic farms in Ghana and Nigeria, where the tropical climate produces leaves with exceptionally high nutrient density. Our processing facilities use low-temperature drying to preserve the nutritional profile, followed by precision milling to 80&ndash;100 mesh particle size &mdash; fine enough for capsules, smoothie powders, and food formulations.
        </p>
        <p>
          An important regulatory note: Moringa oleifera is NOT classified as a Novel Food in the EU, meaning it can be sold freely across European markets. However, following a Salmonella outbreak linked to moringa products in January 2026, FDA scrutiny has increased significantly. Our testing protocols have been enhanced to address this, with every lot tested for Salmonella, E. coli, heavy metals, and total plate count before shipment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Specifications -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-8">Technical Specifications</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <table class="w-full text-left text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-brand-800 text-white">
              <th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Parameter</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Specification</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Protein</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">25 &ndash; 30%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Iron</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">25 &ndash; 30 mg/100g</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Calcium</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">2,000+ mg/100g</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Vitamin A</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">18,000+ IU/100g</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Lead</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">&lt; 0.3 mg/kg</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Cadmium</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">&lt; 0.2 mg/kg</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Total Plate Count (TPC)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">&lt; 10,000 CFU/g</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">E. coli</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Absent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Salmonella</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Absent per 25g</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Mesh Size</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">80 &ndash; 100 mesh</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Available Grades -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-8">Available Grades</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <table class="w-full text-left text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-brand-800 text-white">
              <th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Grade</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Description</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Conventional Powder</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Standard moringa leaf powder. For food products and general supplement use.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Organic Certified (USDA/EU)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Dual-certified organic. For premium supplement brands and organic retailers.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Pharmaceutical Grade</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Tighter microbial limits, lower heavy metal thresholds. For pharma and nutraceutical companies.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Capsule-Ready</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Optimized particle size and flow properties for direct encapsulation. Saves processing time.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-brand-50 border border-brand-200 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-800"><strong>EU Regulatory Note:</strong> Moringa oleifera is NOT classified as a Novel Food in the EU and can be sold freely. No Novel Food authorization required.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Certifications -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-8">Certifications &amp; Documentation</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">Comprehensive certification and testing documentation, with enhanced protocols following the January 2026 FDA Salmonella alert.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          "USDA Organic",
          "EU Organic",
          "HACCP Certified",
          "GMP Certified",
          "Certificate of Analysis (with heavy metals & microbial panel)",
          "Phytosanitary Certificate",
        ].map((cert) => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-gray-200">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-800">{cert}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Packaging & Shipping -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-8">Packaging &amp; Shipping</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 mb-4">Packaging Options</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-600 mt-1">&#8226;</span>
              <span>5 kg food-grade bags (vacuum sealed)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-600 mt-1">&#8226;</span>
              <span>10 kg food-grade bags (vacuum sealed)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-600 mt-1">&#8226;</span>
              <span>25 kg food-grade bags (vacuum sealed)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-600 mt-1">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Custom labeling and private label packaging available</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 mb-4">Key Markets &amp; Transit</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold mt-1">&#9654;</span>
              <span><strong>USA</strong> &mdash; Supplement & health food market</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold mt-1">&#9654;</span>
              <span><strong>Germany &amp; UK</strong> &mdash; Organic retail & pharma</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold mt-1">&#9654;</span>
              <span><strong>Australia &amp; Japan</strong> &mdash; Premium health food</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">FOB Tema/Lagos. All packaging vacuum-sealed to preserve freshness and nutrient content during transit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote Form -->
  <QuoteForm productName="Moringa" />
</Layout>
